:<!--Trigger PerformanceE 100030112: Config/Level/Mission/1000301/Act/Act100030112.json-->
:{{A|VO chapter0 3 staffA 101.ogg}} '''Abraham:''' I need to leave, I need to run from this forsaken...
:{{A|VO chapter0 3 staffA 102.ogg}} '''Abraham:''' No, it's impossible. I can run from yesterday, I can run from today, but tomorrow will always be one step ahead of me...
:{{A|VO chapter0 3 staffA 103.ogg}} '''Abraham:''' Look, the obstacle detection terminal has recorded 142,856 attacks... the next count will be 142,857!
:{{A|VO chapter0 3 staffA 104.ogg}} '''Abraham:''' I know in my heart that when I see that hopelessly beautiful cyclic number... it will mean the poetic end of my life's cycle.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Things will get better.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_100021193-->
::{{A|VO chapter0 3 staffA 105.ogg}} '''Abraham:''' Everyone keeps saying that. "Things will get better, things won't always be this bad."
::{{A|VO chapter0 3 staffA 106.ogg}} '''Abraham:''' Negative... positive... A negative of a negative is a positive.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Life is but a path to death, but not today.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_100021197-->
::{{A|VO chapter0 3 staffA 108.ogg}} '''Abraham:''' Life is but a path to death, but not today... How insightful. Yes, of course! The closer you approach death, the more you appreciate life.
::{{A|VO chapter0 3 staffA 109.ogg}} '''Abraham:''' I will pull myself together. Thank you, that was kind of you.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Life is but a path to death, but not today.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_100021200-->
::{{A|VO chapter0 3 staffA 110.ogg}} '''Abraham:''' How insightful, yes of course. The closer you approach death, the more you appreciate life.
::{{A|VO chapter0 3 staffA 111.ogg}} '''Abraham:''' I will pull myself together. Thank you, that was kind of you.
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
